Added a new "Monitoring" section to the User Guide > Administration documentation. The section covers the three-collector model (logs, metrics, probes), Grafana visualization, SLA / SLO framing with error-budget alerting, low-noise alert recipes, Celery and Job reliability tuning (including the Redis visibility-timeout pitfall), Job-author logging guidance, log forwarding to remote collectors, and Redis / PostgreSQL operational guidance. The existing "Health Checks", "Prometheus Metrics", and "Request Profiling" pages were moved into the new section with redirects from the old paths.
